Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.59,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.63,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.33,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:04.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years have passed\Nsince the Paramount War at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew\Neach completed individual training,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and on their way\Nto the next stage—the New World—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they reached Fishman Island,\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have yet to gather\Nand are stirring things up as a fragmented crew!
