Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That cloud looks like an animal called a "raccoon dog"\Nthat I've seen before in a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that looks like Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!\NChopper is one of my crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crewmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see clearly, it's too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.38,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(440,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(395,440,\1a&H00&)}Ryugu Kingdom\NPort Town of Coral Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.38,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(440,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Ryugu Kingdom\NPort Town of Coral Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, what is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:46.67,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace! Ryugu Palace! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.67,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Border Control HQ, Main Entrance
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.67,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Border Control HQ, Main Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace! This is Border Control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we reach them?\NIs the Transponder Snail sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they coming in flocks to Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know those dangerous people from the Fishman District
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,don't just come here for some shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be remembered as the day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone on Fishman Island\Nis united under one flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All Fishmen, including Merfolk,\Nhave to be like-minded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We must dominate the humans
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,since they're such lowly creatures who can't even breathe in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's correct the mistakes of history now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be the anniversary of our engagement, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hurry.\NLet's get married tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That annoying faction from the Sun Pirates,\NJinbe's group, is not here-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune, the God of the Sea, and the brothers;\NFukaboshi, Ryuboshi, Manboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Much! If we can bring those four under control, Neptune's army can't stand against us-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bite all the soldiers' flesh off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just cut them—whatever you tell me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and begin capturing your objectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ryugu Kingdom falls today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we will dominate the sea floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Forest... I wonder what that place is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking her! Nico Robin of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman! You and your friends\Nare suspects in two ongoing investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First, for multiple counts\Nof Mermaid kidnapping! Second,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you people are suspected of being
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,potential risks to Fishman Island,\Naccording to Madame Sharley's future vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're taking all of the Straw Hats into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.\NAnd did you say "future vision"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You people need to get your brains checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you unashamedly believe in such unscientific things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley's future visions are accurate!\NCome with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you.\NI don't want to miss my bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We have to report...\NShe... got... away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.15,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"Sea Forest"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They had information as I thought. There is a Poneglyph somewhere here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this kingdom holds\Nan important key to the Void Century!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.97,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Ryugu Palace
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.97,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Ryugu Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we always get involved in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop whining, Nami!\NThe battle is on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep attacking us so we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Zoro! We don't wanna get ourselves into more trouble than we already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with pirates fighting pirates?\NThere's no crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, he never learns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, you're barely clinging to life—\Nwhy do you wanna fight so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle this peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they'll give up that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The switch for the gateway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't open it, they'll kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't they get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been training myself since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were people stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there are people even stronger than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shark?\NYou don't feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Megalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a stomach ache, Shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!\NBe careful, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound like I cut them down\Njust for the fun of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you looked like you were enjoying it.\NYou're a natural born manslayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, if you were attacked by pirates,\Nwhat would you do? Serve tea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, serving tea and talking is one way to solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, if you beat them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to find out what they wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying so much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like things are going from bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do most of our crewmates\Ntend to act like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, there's no point even questioning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Luffy-san's met\Nthe Mermaid Princess already. I wanna see her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, untie me! Give me back Shirahoshi-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think we want to kidnap\Nthe Mermaid Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Straw Hat Luffy did it-jamon! Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Luffy-san and Shark-san coming out of the room for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't see the Mermaid Princess with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is not the kind of girl\Nwho just sneaks out on her own-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi is as big as myself-jamon. Someone will notice her if she gets out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The Mermaid Princess is big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a princess-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah-jamon! Maybe, he hid Shirahoshi in Megalo's mouth and took her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making us laugh under these circumstances, King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing? Even if he had the idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose is itching too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, did you catch cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't often catch cold.\NI wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, our captain wouldn't kidnap anybody!\NYou better look for somebody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't think of anybody else!\NIf Shirahoshi doesn't come back safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't have your ship or friends back-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't do that to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like those human pirates pulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunny, are you alright?!\NYou're a super miracle ship just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is like a graveyard of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The tide brings sunken ships here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it ironic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's that kinda place,\Nit receives the blessings of the Sun Tree Eve—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,corals have grown beautifully drawing fish and whales here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! There are a lot of whales and they are so much bigger than the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whales only come to fertile seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying\Nthis magical Sea Forest in the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's hard to believe\Nthat this place is in the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure Tree Adam—it is so valuable. But you built one hell of a ship out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made with the same material\Nas the Pirate King' ship Tom-san made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my greatest design of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the coating.\NCount on me-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you...\NUm... Can I ask your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Den.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Den-san. You don't look much like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Merman—not a cowfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd look like him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.99,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,since you're his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:52.63,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(705,750,\1a&H00&)}Den (Tom's younger brother)\NShipwright and Sea Forest researcher
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.89,0:16:52.63,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}Den (Tom's younger brother)\NShipwright and Sea Forest researcher
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,That's how a human would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Races on earth— family members often look alike, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishmen are a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishmen and Merfolk each have different, ancient genes from their ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:12.88,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"A mother and son"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When an octopus Mermaid gives birth to a shark Merman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that means one of her ancestors\Nwas a shark Merfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so strange when kids don't look like their parents on Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can't understand\Nwhy you humans want to discriminate against...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,those who don't look like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, one of your ancestors was a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Human? Oh, one of your ancestors\Nwas a humanoid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a normal human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, she mentioned you and Iceberg-kun in her letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that old bag Kokoro wrote to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thoughtful old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know everything about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother lived life his own way-don,\Nto the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you traveled all the way here to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a good pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Well, let's just say that I'm a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,\Nsomebody's been sitting there for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's expecting somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't wanna enter the island\Nsince he's a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.39,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(705,750,\1a&H00&)}Entrance to Ryugu Palace
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.39,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\4a&HFF&}Entrance to Ryugu Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.56,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(370,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(325,370,\1a&H00&)}Gateway
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.56,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(370,0)\4a&HFF&}Gateway
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.20,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(255,255)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(210,255,\1a&H00&)\t(1545,1590,\1a&HFF&)}Main Gate
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.20,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(255,255)\4a&HFF&}Main Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.97,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,520)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)\t(2480,2525,\1a&HFF&)}Palace Gate
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.97,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,520)\4a&HFF&}Palace Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.97,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,We have intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you guys get this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!\NI was ready to start a fight right away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but Neptune and all his soldiers are tied up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see a present like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The hateful Vander Decken! You've shown up at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody Jones from the Fishman District!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody? That guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was once a decorated soldier in our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of trap?\NIt's too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had visitors one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lively palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ha! You guys are their accomplices! You let them in, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, we wouldn't be here\Nif you guys didn't invite us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They look formidable!\NWho are those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let us have our arms at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let us fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken!\NSince you've shown up, there is no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who did it! Give me back my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even got married yet.\NIt's too soon for you to say that, Father-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take Shirahoshi?! You'd better tell me she's unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou're talking like the Princess is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit acting dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would Shirahoshi have disappeared from her room all of the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shirahoshi disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my... My daughter-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama, don't lose your temper\Nover his nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. All of the humans that you threw, aimed at the Mermaid Princess, are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Princess Shirahoshi was here\Nat least during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, it doesn't matter if they're lying or not
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because you know how to check where she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Check where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!\NHody, you're a very smart guy! I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is he leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he gonna do?
